"{\"uid\": \"ky3.com-2024-08-09-ozarks-life-springfieldian-planned-logistics-1996-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"SPRINGFIELD, Mo.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 16, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SPRINGFIELD, Mo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\"}, {\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SPRINGFIELD, Mo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Springfield,_Missouri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(KY3) - Inside the Plaza Towers, on the third floor, is an office with quite the proclamation from 28 years ago.\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was very proud of being part of something that is quite unique,\\\" 88-year-old Irwin Cohen said.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 211, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irwin_Cohen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irwin Cohen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irwin_Cohen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irwin_Cohen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cohen now consults companies on transportation issues.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He worked for close to 40 years with New York's Transit Authority.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999946495033677, \"rank\": 5.345367606889656e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew all about elevated rail or trains in tunnels.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That lead him to Atlanta in the mid-90s, where he was the Director of Car Transportation for the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999999165539, \"rank\": 8.330989933456935e-11, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly I understood the impact of moving people,\\\" Irwin said, \\\"but the Olympics turned my head.\\\"\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years before the Olympic Games in Atlanta, Irwin was hired to help plan the logistics in Georgia.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999999165539, \"rank\": 8.330989933456935e-11, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}, {\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9993034975423711, \"rank\": 0.0005586913440393098, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His experience, paired with his calm demeanor, made him the perfect person to put in charge of the MARTA rail system.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The trains would have to be prepared to move a million fans a day.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We took out seats (from the train cars); it's like moving cattle,\\\" Irwin said.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that car is resting on the truck.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's living on the springs.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(There is) no cushioning, none.\\\"\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the cars themselves to the personnel, Irwin was the lead of moving fans and Atlantans.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also had the idea of putting technicians at the stations so if an issue happened, it could be fixed quickly.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had a derailment during the Olympics and I needed that like a hole in the head,\\\" Irwin said.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But thanks to his planning, the train was back on track in an hour and 15 minutes.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Irwin had the city's rail moving like a well-oiled machine.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Irwin was a go-to voice during those Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years of preparation for two weeks of competition.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only thing I could remember is the opening,\\\" Irwin said, \\\"and you know why?\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9997810197032264, \"rank\": 0.00021893102689744134, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Irwin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Muhammad Ali.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999819962406012, \"rank\": 1.2426575876046887e-05, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I never forgot that.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was only thing that just made me cry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not see a darn thing other than Muhammad Ali, people, and the trains.\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999819962406012, \"rank\": 1.2426575876046887e-05, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I missed a lot.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was happy to be part of that, because if you are part of the Olympics, it never goes away.\\\"\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To report a correction or typo, please emaildigitalnews@ky3.com.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please include the article info in the subject line of the email.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": []